#- 22.11.               Nr.3§0
§4§l§n    World News     §0
§0§lGroundhog Day!§0
§0Last Sunday the world stood still: After ttk2 messed up one of the plugin parameters, the Server was down all day! Once it was back up, many people reported having extreme deja-vus!
#- §lRágnàrök paused for now.§0
§0After HCF incaders and Speedcreepers wreaking havoc for a week, Based ttk2 has delayed the end of the world as we know it (for now). As for how long it may remain as peaceful as now is unclear. Meanwhile, the sun has come back
