#- 22.11.           Nr.3§0
§4§l§n      Bielefeld     §0
§0§lMain Station completed!§0
§0The Main Station of Bielefeld has been finished after 6 months of construction and will officially be opened with a ceremony held on Wednesday at 8 pm. Dont be late!
#- 22.11.              Nr. 3§0
§4§l§n     Local News    §0
§0§l§nNeustria§0
§0A new town named Rochefurt has been founded. Its location lies at x2300 x8300§0
§0-------------§0
§0A jihadi has burned down the Tree of the Wooden House, an important Gov. Building of Neustria.
#- A memorial has been built at its place.§0
